kw.name: Disconnect From Postgresql
kw.doc: Close active PostgreSQL connection. You will have to manually open or switch to a new connection. Due to how ConnectionCache works, connection's index and alias are not removed from cache, so you are able to switch to closed connection, if it was closed with Disconnect from Postgresql. It will still remain closed though.
